# Exclude Storybook from Turbo's default build pipeline
# Storybook is a development/documentation tool and should only be built explicitly
#
# To run Storybook:
# - pnpm storybook (dev server)
# - pnpm storybook:build (production build)
# - pnpm --filter @magneto365-ui/storybook dev
# - pnpm --filter @magneto365-ui/storybook build
#
# This file ensures Storybook is never included in:
# - pnpm build (only builds packages/*)
# - pnpm test (only tests packages/*)
# - pnpm lint (only lints packages/*)
*
